response.overview: January 25th, 2009 :: Season 8 premieres with the vacant Young Lions Cup up for grabs in Chikara’s first-ever ladder match between Jimmy “Equinox” Olsen and Vin Gerard! UltraMantis Black has something to reveal. The Colony cash in their three points, and challenge for los Campeonatos de Parejas! Matches featured:  1. F.I.S.T. vs The Future Is Now  2. The Roughnecks vs Incoherence  3. Daizee Haze vs Sara Del Rey  4. The Order Of The Neo-Solar Temple vs Jigsaw, Mike Quackenbush  5. The UnStable vs Cheech Hernandez & KC "Cloudy" Day  6. Los Ice Creams vs The Fabulous Two  7. Eddie Kingston vs Delirious  8. Campeonatos de Parejas Match The Colony vs The Osirian Portal  9. Young Lions Cup Ladder Match Equinox vs Vin Gerard.
response.title: Chikara Revelation X
